//dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/31.mp3","time_start":74.82,"time_end":76.89},{"position":32,"content":"You don't have to.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/32.mp3","time_start":76.89,"time_end":78.3},{"position":33,"content":"You can get a meal in the hotel if you want to,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/33.mp3","time_start":78.3,"time_end":80.77},{"position":34,"content":"and there's no charge for it so you might as well.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/34.mp3","time_start":80.77,"time_end":83.61},{"position":35,"content":"Oh good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/35.mp3","time_start":83.61,"time_end":84.65},{"position":36,"content":"Yes, so let's see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/36.mp3","time_start":84.65,"time_end":85.76},{"position":37,"content":"I'd get er..., 221, no, no, £231 a week?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/37.mp3","time_start":85.76,"time_end":91.27},{"position":38,"content":"You'd also get tips.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/38.mp3","time_start":91.27,"time_end":92.96},{"position":39,"content":"Our guests tend to be quite generous.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/39.mp3","time_start":92.96,"time_end":95.34},{"position":40,"content":"Erm, is there a uniform?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/40.mp3","time_start":95.5,"time_end":97.58},{"position":41,"content":"What about clothes?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/41.mp3","time_start":97.58,"time_end":98.99},{"position":42,"content":"Yes, I forgot to mention that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/42.mp3","time_start":98.99,"time_end":101.22},{"position":43,"content":"You need to wear a white shirt, just a plain one,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/43.mp3","time_start":101.22,"time_end":104.16},{"position":44,"content":"and dark trousers.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/44.mp3","time_start":104.16,"time_end":105.51},{"position":45,"content":"You know, not green or anything like that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/45.mp3","time_start":105.51,"time_end":107.94},{"position":46,"content":"And we don't supply those.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/46.mp3","time_start":107.94,"time_end":109.58},{"position":47,"content":"That's okay, I've got trousers,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/47.mp3","time_start":109.58,"time_end":111.42},{"position":48,"content":"I'd just have to buy a couple of shirts.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/48.mp3","time_start":111.42,"time_end":113.29},{"position":49,"content":"What about anything else?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/49.mp3","time_start":113.29,"time_end":114.46},{"position":50,"content":"Do I need a waistcoat or anything?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/50.mp3","time_start":114.63,"time_end":116.32},{"position":51,"content":"You have to wear a jacket, but the hotel lends you that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/51.mp3","time_start":116.32,"time_end":119.25},{"position":52,"content":"I see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/52.mp3","time_start":119.25,"time_end":120.02},{"position":53,"content":"One last thing - I don't know what the starting date is.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/53.mp3","time_start":120.5,"time_end":124.17},{"position":54,"content":"Just a minute, I think it's sometime around the end of June.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/54.mp3","time_start":124.17,"time_end":129.15},{"position":55,"content":"Yes, the 28th, in time for the summer.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/55.mp3","time_start":129.15,"time_end":132.39},{"position":56,"content":"That's great. I'm available from the 10th.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/56.mp3","time_start":132.39,"time_end":134.57},{"position":57,"content":"Oh good.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-8-test-4-part-1-2023-07-27-13-01-28/57.mp3","time_start":134.57,"time_end":135.87},{"position":58,"content":"Well, if you can call again you need to speak to the Service Manager.","audi